        <mxCell id="legend_text" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=13;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacingLeft=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Region Failover (~10 seconds)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• ARC Routing Control ON = us-east-1 active (blue solid path)&lt;br&gt;• ARC Routing Control OFF = us-east-2 active (green dashed path)&lt;br&gt;• Lambda@Edge queries ARC data plane (5 regional endpoints, no single-region dependency)&lt;br&gt;• Memory replication: event-driven via S3 + SNS + SQS + Lambda (~10-15s)" vertex="1">
